<item>
            <title>[FLINK-3735] Embedded SQL union should fail during translation</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-3735</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The Table API currently only supports union all and embedded SQL queries translate both union and union all to union all. We should only generate a valid plan for union all.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
